Description: Add drag-and-drop behavior to Shiny Apps and gadgets.  
    Add ranking, sorting and bucketing question types to `learnr` tutorials. 
    The package creates an 'htmlwidget' by wrapping the 'sortable.js' 
    JavaScript library.
